lead_paragraph: Arizona ace Zack Greinke got off to a rough start and lost again, with Kris Bryant and the Chicago Cubs beating the Diamondbacks 4-2 Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Greinke Roughed Up Again, Cubs Beat Diamondbacks
